OL,6,FA senior manager from Manchester stole
OL,7,Falmost #63,000 from her employer to
OL,8,Ffund her gambling and cocaine
OL,9,Faddictions.
OL,11,FManchester Minshull Street Crown Court
OL,12,Fheard that Laura Barnard dipped into
OL,13,Fthe company's accounts over the course
OL,14,Fof year - between August 2021 and
OL,15,FAugust 2022 - while working at
OL,16,FThinkmoney as a senior project manager.
OL,18,FShe developed a good relationship with
OL,19,Fher employer, the court heard, and her
OL,20,Fbarrister claimed they were 'like
OL,21,Ffamily'.
