OL,3,CManager stole nearly #63,000 from
OL,4,Cemployer to fund gambling and cocaine
OL,6,F39-year-old Barnard, of Littler
OL,7,FAvenue, Chorlton, Manchester,
OL,8,Fpreviously worked as a project manager
OL,9,Fbefore she was promoted to a more
OL,10,Fsenior role with a salary of #65,000.
OL,12,FThe court was told that she was
OL,13,Fauthorised to carry out test
OL,14,Ftransactions - of small sums - to her
OL,15,Faccounts to make sure new systems were
OL,16,Fworking correctly, but that she was
OL,17,Fexpected to return the money.
OL,19,FBut she began exploiting the process,
OL,20,Fdisguising illicit transfers to her
OL,21,Faccounts as 'goodwill payments'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
