OL,3,CManager stole nearly #63,000 from
OL,4,Cemployer to fund gambling and cocaine
OL,6,FBarnard was finally caught when the
OL,7,Fcompany spotted she had made payments
OL,8,Fwhile on holiday and outside her
OL,9,Fworking hours, but the court heard
OL,10,Fthat she continued to make payments to
OL,11,Fherself even after she was rumbled.
OL,13,FIn all she made 517 transactions with
OL,14,Fa total value of #62,793.
OL,16,FShe was sentenced at Manchester
OL,17,FMinshull Street Crown Court after
OL,18,Fpleading guilty to fraud by abuse of
OL,19,Fposition; and concealing criminal
OL,20,Fproperty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
