OL,3,CManager stole nearly #63,000 from
OL,4,Cemployer to fund gambling and cocaine
OL,6,FProsecutor Lisa Boocock described
OL,7,FBarnard as a 'trusted member of
OL,8,Fstaff', adding: "She began
OL,9,Ftransferring sums that were far larger
OL,10,Fthan were needed, she used 14 test
OL,11,Faccounts to send money. The defendant
OL,12,Fwould also purport to make goodwill
OL,13,Fpayments. Using these goodwill
OL,14,Fpayments gave her an opportunity to
OL,15,Fdisguise payments.
