OL,6,F"She had a significant gambling and
OL,7,Fcocaine habit on which she was
OL,8,Fspending a significant proportion of
OL,9,Fthe money." She added that after being
OL,10,Ffound out, Barnard said she 'would pay
OL,11,Fit back'.
OL,13,F"She returned around #2,000," Ms
OL,14,FBoocock added. "The vast majority of
OL,15,Fthe money was never returned."
