OL,3,CManager stole nearly #63,000 from
OL,4,Cemployer to fund gambling and cocaine
OL,6,FThe court heard that shortly after her
OL,7,Farrest, Barnard found out she was
OL,8,Fpregnant and Barrister James Hudson,
OL,9,Fdefending, told the court: "The birth
OL,10,Fof her son has been a huge stabilising
OL,11,Ffactor in her life." He said his
OL,12,Fclients was 'genuinely remorseful for
OL,13,Fher offending against a company which
OL,14,Fshe described as being like family'.
OL,16,FBarnard was sentenced to 18 months in
OL,17,Fprison, suspended for 18 months. She
OL,18,Fwas ordered to complete 180 hours of
OL,19,Funpaid work and 15 rehabilitation days.
